{"id": 1165, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于各种各样的“套餐”，你有什么要吐槽的?", "description": "最气人的应该是“套餐价格等于其中单品价格相加”这件事。（题图来自：Andrew Lebedinsky）", "record_count": 3114, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160810205708eOBNTLlEYUm7yXh3.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-12T03:00:37Z", "options": [{"id": 106853, "content": "能够有按照个人的订制就好了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109759}, {"id": 106854, "content": "套餐，约等于套路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 106855, "content": "每次我就偏不买套餐！", "image": "img/option/option_pic/20160812111821V3hD8LTRpXNKdOoe4.jpg", "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397696}, {"id": 106859, "content": "套路都是套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707539}, {"id": 106862, "content": "买了之后发现被坑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707539}, {"id": 106877, "content": "不搭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686442}, {"id": 106884, "content": "先下套，后用餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712762}, {"id": 106889, "content": "1，给你一个选择，接盘与否全在自己。2，套餐打造全新的生活方式。3，至于套餐价格等同于单品价格相加，设定活动的人和消费者还有自己开了一个玩笑。我们要允许错误发生，社会才会进步❤️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676351}, {"id": 106892, "content": "永远不是自己的best choise", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693214}, {"id": 106898, "content": "难吃的居多，好吃的一点点。分量足", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688416}, {"id": 107008, "content": "套餐就是让你花更多的钱，薄利多销吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673825}, {"id": 107009, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659221}, {"id": 107010, "content": "哈哈哈更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659221}, {"id": 107011, "content": "套餐就是商店提供的永远比你想买的多得多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126276}, {"id": 107012, "content": "看似实惠实质是套路中翻套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688064}, {"id": 107013, "content": "这是强制消费吗。。。。？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713171}, {"id": 107014, "content": "总有一款你最爱，总有另一款你不需要。合起来就是套餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713173}, {"id": 107015, "content": "我就要自己单点⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 107016, "content": "便宜点才考虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200213}, {"id": 107017, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107018, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107019, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 109323, "content": "要么太多要么太少，你找到一个看上去不错的实际不咋地", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725248}, {"id": 107020, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 113932, "content": "不能换饮料！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746938}, {"id": 107021, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107022, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107023, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107024, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107025, "content": "套餐永远是里面有最喜欢的东西同样也有最讨厌的东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107026, "content": "最喜欢的和最不喜欢的搭配就成了套餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107027, "content": "最喜欢的和最不喜欢的搭配就成了套餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704654}, {"id": 107029, "content": "可能是因为大家还是有啥吃啥的习惯吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708977}, {"id": 107285, "content": "单买的都比套餐便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 107030, "content": "可能是因为大家还是有啥吃啥的习惯吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708977}, {"id": 107031, "content": "总有些不大想吃的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565088}, {"id": 107032, "content": "S手机套装。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708442}, {"id": 107033, "content": "每次都要将就着买来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686544}, {"id": 107034, "content": "要是能不同品类自由组合就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692929}, {"id": 108058, "content": "是弟弟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716138}, {"id": 107035, "content": "就是喜欢单点，任性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710507}, {"id": 107036, "content": "套餐里总是有你非常想要的和非常不想要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713210}, {"id": 107037, "content": "选择困难症患者的福音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713213}, {"id": 107293, "content": "其实并没有便宜多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141957}, {"id": 107038, "content": "套餐里总有一样你不喜欢吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514595}, {"id": 107039, "content": "永远算不过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698323}, {"id": 107295, "content": "套餐包含着不喜欢的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635119}, {"id": 107040, "content": "不买套餐觉得贵，但套餐却吃不完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693989}, {"id": 107041, "content": "一切以实物为准", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713223}, {"id": 107042, "content": "不管用的还是吃的，总不是自己最想要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590959}]}